acroscopic photonic states with very large\nsqueezing, with over 90% less noise (10 dB) than the classical value associated\nwith shot noise.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 2 Nov 2022 23:22:38 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 10 Nov 2022 14:11:58 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-03-29"}
