ulk\nproperties and coupling between the opposite hemispheres. The study indicates\nthat the two hemispheric data sets differ, but some dependency could be\npresent.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 3 Nov 2022 08:48:18 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-11-30"}
