_{\\rm c}$ as the quantum critical point for\nthe transition of the spin system in BiCoPO$_5$ to the quantum disordered state\nat stronger fields.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 3 Nov 2022 09:08:36 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-11-04"}
