 of awareness and immersion is important in virtual reality based\nteleoperation, considering the safety and robustness of the control system. An\nexperiment shows the effectiveness of our solution.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 3 Nov 2022 12:29:14 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-11-04"}
