ogram. We also explore the mathematical properties of the\nBuchdahl-inspired metrics in the limit of small k and in the region around the\ncoordinate origin.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 2 Nov 2022 17:46:23 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-11-04"}
