ssentially, the\ninverse of the implosion process. Both of these hypotheses are testable with\nnon-potential coronal field extrapolations.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 3 Nov 2022 15:43:53 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 4 Nov 2022 14:44:20 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Tue, 8 Nov 2022 16:53:22 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-11-09"}
